flowchart TD
    Start[Function Call] --> Check{Result?}
    Check -->|Ok| Continue[Continue Execution]
    Check -->|Err| QMark{Using ?}
    QMark -->|Yes| Return[Return Early with Err]
    QMark -->|No| Match[Pattern Match]
    Match --> HandleOk[Handle Ok case]
    Match --> HandleErr[Handle Err case]

    Continue --> Next[Next Operation]
